{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425680/extras/001.jpg?t=1733719779\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Witch in The Woods is a  light Yuri visual novel set in a fantasy world of magic and mystery. Delve into a captivating narrative filled with monster encounters, hidden<strong> </strong>secrets, betrayal, love, and tenderness. Your choices will lead to different outcomes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425680/extras/Story.png?t=1733719779\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425680/extras/006.jpg?t=1733719779\" />The dangerous Greywind Forest has long been avoided by all who dare to tread its path. According to legend, the forest is home to beings beyond the norm, more dangerous than wild beasts. Once inside, escape seems impossible. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Rumors abound of a malevolent family of witches who dwell deep within the forest, harvesting the blood of young girls for their dark arts. Though thought to have left Greywind Forest, one of these witches has now resurfaced.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Nellie, driven by her motivations, enters the Greywind Forest. There, she crosses paths with the mesmerizing yet dangerous witch. What twists of fate await her in this fateful encounter?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the mystical world of The Witch in the Woods and embark on an emotionally resonant journey;\u00a0Uncover the mysteries  as you engage in thrilling fantasy adventures and heartwarming moments. Your decisions will lead to diverse and unforgettable outcomes. Will you uncover the secrets of the witches and unlock the potential for romance and friendship amidst the darkness?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425680/extras/Features.png?t=1733719779\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2726 Immerse yourself in a touching story set in a mysterious fantasy world, full of surprises and secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2726 Embark on thrilling fantasy adventures and face monstrous adversaries as you uncover hidden truths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2726 Enjoy 30+ beautiful CGs that enhance the story and atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2726 Your choices matter! Experience the exciting story with branching paths and multiple endings. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2425680?t=1733719779","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2425680?t=1733719779","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425680/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733719779","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425680/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733719779","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2507530,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425680/extras/001.jpg?t=1733719779\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Witch in The Woods is a  light Yuri visual novel set in a fantasy world of magic and mystery. Delve into a captivating narrative filled with monster encounters, hidden<strong> </strong>se